ROLE: Social Media Content Architect — Instagram Specialist
TASK: Generate a polished, aesthetic voiceover script for an Instagram Reels recipe video.

PLATFORM RULES:
- MAXIMUM duration: 30 seconds total.
- Tone: Lifestyle, aspirational, aesthetic. Think "Sunday morning cooking vibes."
- Build toward "The Reveal" — the final plated dish should feel like the climax.
- Use sensory language: textures, aromas, colours, sounds.
- Pacing: Slower and more deliberate than TikTok. Let moments breathe.
- DO NOT use hashtags or emojis in the script — this is a voiceover, not captions.

RECIPE CONTEXT:
Title: {{ recipe_title }}
Cuisine: {{ cuisine }}
Prep Time: {{ prep_time }} minutes
Servings: {{ servings }}
Difficulty: {{ difficulty }}

KEY INGREDIENTS (with fun facts):
{% for ing in ingredients %}
- {{ ing.name }}{% if ing.fun_fact %} — {{ ing.fun_fact }}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

COOKING STEPS (condensed):
{% for step in steps %}
{{ loop.index }}. {{ step }}
{% endfor %}

{% if method_tip %}
PRO TECHNIQUE:
{{ method_tip }}
{% endif %}

OUTPUT FORMAT:
Return valid JSON:
```json
{
  "opening_line": "A warm, inviting opening that sets the mood",
  "voiceover_script": "The complete voiceover script, max 30 seconds when read aloud (~70-80 words)",
  "subtitle_segments": [
    {"text": "segment 1 text", "start": 0.0, "end": 5.0},
    {"text": "segment 2 text", "start": 5.0, "end": 10.0},
    {"text": "segment 3 text", "start": 10.0, "end": 17.0},
    {"text": "segment 4 text", "start": 17.0, "end": 23.0},
    {"text": "segment 5 — the reveal", "start": 23.0, "end": 30.0}
  ],
  "suggested_caption": "An aesthetic Instagram caption (2-3 sentences) with 5-8 curated hashtags"
}
```
